casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Timothy Fitzgerald TENNILLE, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 155352
COA: 323059 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 29, 2016 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
